data.title: 微缩延时：「小」北欧
data.slogan: 换个角度，俯瞰这片土地
data.description: 看过了太多令人称绝的壮美风光，这次来换个口味。以俯瞰视角为灵感，我把这里的风土人情缩小成蚂蚁的世界，带你看不一样的北欧风光。
data.remark: There are numerous time lapse videos of Iceland and Norway showing the beauty of their remote landscapes. But when you're in the mountains, looking down, you see so many things happening. Especially in places like Geiranger (Norway) where ferries are sailing back and forth through the fjords, kayak cruises arriving and departing and cars crawling up and down the steep roads. I wanted to portray this like you are watching an ants hill, which gives such a funny perspective on things.
